# SmartFlow CRM - UI Patterns & Design Specifications

## Spacing System

### Base Unit
```css
/* Base unit: 4px */
--base-unit: 0.25rem;
```

### Spacing Scale
```css
/* Micro Spacing (for icons, tight layouts) */
--space-micro: calc(var(--base-unit) * 1);    /* 4px */
--space-tiny: calc(var(--base-unit) * 2);     /* 8px */

/* Component Spacing */
--space-small: calc(var(--base-unit) * 3);    /* 12px */
--space-medium: calc(var(--base-unit) * 4);   /* 16px */
--space-large: calc(var(--base-unit) * 6);    /* 24px */

/* Layout Spacing */
--space-xl: calc(var(--base-unit) * 8);       /* 32px */
--space-2xl: calc(var(--base-unit) * 12);     /* 48px */
--space-3xl: calc(var(--base-unit) * 16);     /* 64px */

/* Section Spacing */
--space-section: calc(var(--base-unit) * 24);  /* 96px */
```

### Spacing Applications
```css
/* Component Internal Spacing */
.card {
  padding: var(--space-medium);
  gap: var(--space-small);
}

/* Layout Spacing */
.section {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-section);
}

/* Grid Gaps */
.grid {
  gap: var(--space-large);
}
```

## UI Patterns

### Card Patterns
```css
/* Standard Card */
.card-standard {
  padding: var(--space-medium);
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: var(--neutral-100);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}

/* Glass Card */
.card-glass {
  padding: var(--space-medium);
  border-radius: 16px;
  background: var(--glass-bg);
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
}

/* Interactive Card */
.card-interactive {
  transition: var(--transition-base);
  cursor: pointer;
}

.card-interactive:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
}
```

### Form Patterns
```css
/* Form Groups */
.form-group {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-tiny);
}

/* Input with Label */
.input-group {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-micro);
}

/* Search Pattern */
.search-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
}

.search-input {
  padding-left: calc(var(--space-medium) + 24px); /* Icon space */
}

.search-icon {
  position: absolute;
  left: var(--space-small);
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
}
```

### Navigation Patterns
```css
/* Sidebar Navigation */
.nav-sidebar {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-small);
}

.nav-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-small);
  padding: var(--space-small) var(--space-medium);
  border-radius: 8px;
}

/* Breadcrumb */
.breadcrumb {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-small);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
}
```

