## Design References & Patterns

### Dashboard Layout
```css
/* Main Layout */
.dashboard-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* Content Area */
.content-area {
  padding: var(--space-large);
  background: var(--neutral-100);
}

/* Stats Grid */
.stats-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-medium);
}
```

### Common UI Elements
```css
/* Action Bar */
.action-bar {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: var(--space-medium) 0;
}

/* Data Table */
.table-container {
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
}

/* Pagination */
.pagination {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-tiny);
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: var(--space-large);
}
```

### Interactive States
```css
/* Button States */
.button {
  &:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  &:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  
  &:focus {
    outline: 2px solid var(--primary-blue-light);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
}

/* Input States */
.input {
  &:focus {
    border-color: var(--primary-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(45, 50, 130, 0.1);
  }
  
  &:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary-blue-light);
  }
}
```

